exceptions.tactic: apply provable_multi_imp_weaken with (x := multi_imp xs2 y).
exceptions.exn: In environment L : Language minL : MinimumLanguage L Gamma : Provable L minAX : MinimumAxiomatization L Gamma xs1, xs2 : list expr y : expr Unable to unify "(let (provable) := Gamma in provable) (multi_imp ?M1963 (multi_imp xs2 y) --> multi_imp ?M1963 ?M1965)" with "(let (provable) := Gamma in provable) (multi_imp xs2 y --> multi_imp (xs1 ++ xs2) y)".

original: intros xs1 xs2 y. intros H. apply provable_multi_imp_weaken with (x := multi_imp xs2 y). apply H.
